From 55c3912f2fbf4a6b0d583bd67c3350f1ec6ed0b3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Karsten Sperling <ksperling@apple.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Oct 2025 22:13:18 +1300
Subject: [PATCH] Ubus: Miscellaneous tweaks

- Rename AppendResult and make it usable with different buffers
- Make ParseLong a free functions
- Add DeviceRoleToString that avoid strcpy / buffer in HandleState
- Make mHost a reference instead of a pointer
- Replace a final sprintf with snprintf
- Add IgnoreError to async / best effort otThreadSendDiagnosticGet
- Tidy up includes
---
